> [calls roland_run_team({ goal: "add complete notification system: email (SendGrid), SMS (Twilio), and in-app with event-driven delivery and opt-out support" })]
> ✅ Started. Wave 1 planning now. I'll check back when it completes — or call `pm_standup()` any time for live status.

**Checking status:**
> User: @roland what's the status?
>
> Roland: [calls pm_standup()]
> [displays board snapshot]
